des:
Cleveland Indians baseball trivia was amassed by a long time fan. This new skill brings Indians baseball trivia into your home year round.

Cleveland Indians baseball trivia is great for the entire family! Play with or against each other and see who really knows the Indians.

New trivia is constantly being added to the skill so keep coming back to play!

This skill is not sponsored by MLB or the Cleveland Indians. This is a fan created skill.
